831
01:26:06,335 --> 01:26:08,803
- You said if I delivered...
- Shut up.

832
01:26:09,072 --> 01:26:12,564
- You're going back to the population.
- Population?

833
01:26:12,775 --> 01:26:16,108
You can't do this to me, warden.
You can't do this.

834
01:26:16,345 --> 01:26:19,439
I snitched him off.
They're gonna kill me. I'm finished.

835
01:26:19,615 --> 01:26:21,480
Tough.

836
01:26:21,851 --> 01:26:25,651
Look, I came through, goddamn it!
We had a deal!

837
01:26:27,990 --> 01:26:30,652
