Take it down!

938
01:38:34,583 --> 01:38:36,778
I ain't doing life for nothing.

939
01:38:38,053 --> 01:38:40,283
Come on. Lean on it, man!

940
01:38:40,489 --> 01:38:43,322
They're gonna break that door down.

941
01:38:43,559 --> 01:38:46,426
And they're going to take
your skull apart!

942
01:38:46,595 --> 01:38:49,655
You're going to beg me
to let them kill you.

943
01:38:50,032 --> 01:38:52,432
- Come on, break it down!
- Meissner!

944
01:38:53,936 --> 01:38:55,995
Harder, man. Harder!

945
01:39:00,042 --> 01:39:02,237
Come on, lean on it.

946
01:39:02,744 --> 01:39:04,336
No!

947
01:39:06,181 --> 01:39:07,739
No!

948
01:39:09,852 --> 01:39:11,410
Take out the glass!

949
01:39:14,623 --> 01:39:16,682
Shoot! Shoot me!

950
01:39:16,859 --> 01:39:18,326
- Don't shoot!
- Shoot!

951
01:39:18,527 --> 01:39:20,961
He has his hand taped to the lever.

952
01:39:21,430 --> 01:39:22,897
No!

953
01:39:23,398 --> 01:39:27,425
- Don't shoot!
- Hold your fire. Hold your fire.

954
01:39:27,603 --> 01:39:28,934
Come on, shoot!

955
01:39:31,373 --> 01:39:32,931
Hold your fire!

956
01:39:35,911 --> 01:39:38,539
Relax. Just relax.

957
01:39:39,381 --> 01:39:42,782
Glad you're here, Meissner. This
wouldn't be official without witnesses.

958
01:39:42,951 --> 01:39:47,945
He's bluffing. He's wants me to take
responsibility for his escape attempt.

959
01:39:48,223 --> 01:39:51,954
I don't want a confession.
You set me up. You set everything up!

960
01:39:52,127 --> 01:39:56,461
- I don't know what you're talking about.
- I'm talking about Chink Weber!

961
01:39:56,665 --> 01:39:58,360
The goons.

962
01:39:58,800 --> 01:40:01,667
The cop that was gonna rape Melissa.

963
01:40:02,471 --> 01:40:03,768
Dallas.

964
01:40:04,740 --> 01:40:07,106
The killing of the kid.

965
01:40:08,243 --> 01:40:10,234
Guilty on all counts.

966
01:40:10,412 --> 01:40:15,577
Prove it! That's your problem.
You can't prove anything.

967
01:40:15,751 --> 01:40:20,313
I don't have to prove nothing.
I came here for an execution.

968
01:40:20,489 --> 01:40:23,788
I demand to be released from here!

969
01:40:24,826 --> 01:40:26,259
No!

970
01:40:26,428 --> 01:40:30,888
Don't do it, Leone. Don't do it.
Take it easy.

971
01:40:31,600 --> 01:40:34,899
You deserve payback.

972
01:40:35,103 --> 01:40:36,502
Frank!

973
01:40:38,674 --> 01:40:40,665
Please, Frank.

974
01:40:41,944 --> 01:40:45,675
Don't kill me. It's true.

975
01:40:48,684 --> 01:40:52,176
I confess, Mr. Meissner.

976
01:40:52,454 --> 01:40:55,321
Everything that he said was true.

977
01:40:55,557 --> 01:40:58,424
I set him up. Everything.

978
01:41:02,164 --> 01:41:03,631
Please.

979
01:41:04,967 --> 01:41:07,162
Don't kill me.

980
01:41:08,670 --> 01:41:09,864
Don't...

981
01:41:10,572 --> 01:41:16,010
See you in hell, Drumgoole.

982
01:41:32,894 --> 01:41:35,328
Works better with this.

983
01:41:37,265 --> 01:41:39,631
Take him to the hole, Mr. Meissner.

984
01:41:40,002 --> 01:41:44,098
Mr. Braden, take the prisoner
to the hole.

985
01:41:44,373 --> 01:41:46,204
- Cuff him.
- Yes, sir.

986
01:41:46,475 --> 01:41:50,741
Somebody get me
out of this chair.

987
01:41:52,247 --> 01:41:53,680
Come on.

988
01:41:58,120 --> 01:42:02,716
Thank you, Mr. Meissner.
I said take him to the hole.

989
01:42:02,891 --> 01:42:04,722
I can't do that.

990
01:42:05,427 --> 01:42:07,224
Take the warden into custody.

991
01:42:07,429 --> 01:42:10,523
- I said take him. What are you doing?
- Cuff him.

992
01:42:10,799 --> 01:42:16,203
Stop it! I am warden of this institution,
and you will obey... Stop that!

993
01:42:16,638 --> 01:42:21,905
That was just a stupid confession to
try and save my life. Are you crazy?

994
01:42:22,310 --> 01:42:24,540
No, but you are.

995
01:42:24,813 --> 01:42:29,944
Until this matter's resolved in a judicial
inquiry, you'll remain in our custody.

996
01:42:32,287 --> 01:42:34,949
I'll have your ass for this.

997
01:42:35,223 --> 01:42:38,715
I'll have your ass.

998
01:42:39,761 --> 01:42:41,422
Move him!

999
01:42:52,841 --> 01:42:55,469
I only wanted to do my time, captain.

1000
01:42:55,911 --> 01:42:58,402
You'll get your chance.

1001
01:42:58,580 --> 01:43:00,673
Move him.

1002
01:43:20,502 --> 01:43:22,595
Hey, Ernie.

1003
01:43:22,771 --> 01:43:24,636
Hang in there, Frank.

1004
01:43:25,006 --> 01:43:26,496
Hey, Frank?

1005
01:43:26,675 --> 01:43:28,666
- Eclipse.
- Take care.

1006
01:43:28,844 --> 01:43:31,472
You too. Thanks a lot, big man.

1007
01:43:31,646 --> 01:43:34,843
Yeah. That okay?

1008
01:43:35,016 --> 01:43:36,779
It's all right.

1009
01:43:39,154 --> 01:43:43,955
Got this one from
Fidel Castro himself.

1010
01:43:46,161 --> 01:43:48,823
- See you, big man.
- Okay.

1011
01:44:08,850 --> 01:44:10,750
Hold it.

1012
01:44:11,052 --> 01:44:13,885
Crack the outside!

1013
01:44:14,756 --> 01:44:18,624
- Know what I'll miss most about you?
- What's that?

1014
01:44:19,494 --> 01:44:22,258
Your incredible smile.

1015
01:44:33,642 --> 01:44:37,510
- Take care of yourself, Leone.
- Thanks, captain.

1016
01:44:48,890 --> 01:44:50,050
Lock 'em!

